    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm waiting for something that's never coming back. like i'm stuck in this constant, dull ache and there's no light at the end of it. honestly, sometimes i just think... why even keep trying to fight this? it feels like the only thing left to do is just stop fighting it and let go. does that even make sense? to just want everything to stop?",
